<p>I have played D1, D2, EQ and WoW(I mention d1 and d2 b/c they are both pvp games like WoW...) <br /> <br /> <br />EQ is more group and raid based....much more end game stuff EQ will always be my favorite game ever.......but it got old. <br /> <br />WoW is more solo....you can lvl from 1 to 60 solo with any class.&nbsp;&nbsp;It is very &quot;quest&quot; oriented. It is also very much like d2.....it is all about the PvP(If you play WoW and join a PvE server I will ***** slap you from now till forever.......WoW=PvPMMO.......)  The end game stuff right now isn't very good.......The end game raid encounters(minus MC boos raggy.....) are not like EQ raids they are easier.  The raiding is also much more primitive(you will find 99% of guilds to /ran  rolls on all loot =/ hardly any guilds use DKP.......I am trying like a SOB to get my guild to move to DKP....)  all in all it is an amazing game full of new stuff and new encounters. <br /> <br /> <br />I ****in love it <br /> <br /> <br />Oh BTW far and away <br /> <br />EQ&gt;WoW&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;Poop on a stick&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;FFXI&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;nasty runny poo on a stick&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;&gt;EQII <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Fri M